SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> 
        || '::' || SUBSTRING("CDPOS"."TABKEY", 1, 3)
        || '::' || SUBSTRING("CDPOS"."TABKEY", 4, 10)                                AS "ObjectID",
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || "CDPOS"."TABKEY" || '::' || "CDPOS"."TABNAME" || '::' || "CDPOS"."FNAME"
        || '::' || "CDPOS"."CHANGENR" || '::' || "CDPOS"."CHNGIND"                AS "ID",
    CAST("CDHDR"."UDATE" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("CDHDR"."UTIME" AS DATE),
                    "CDHDR"."UTIME") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                          AS "Time",
    CASE
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'BTGEW' THEN 'TotalWeight'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'BZIRK' THEN 'SalesDistrict'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'GEWEI' THEN 'WeightUnit'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'KODAT' THEN 'PlannedPickingDate'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'LFART' THEN 'DeliveryType'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'LFDAT' THEN 'DeliveryDate'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'NTGEW' THEN 'NetWeight'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'PODAT' AND "CDPOS"."VALUE_OLD" <> '00000000' THEN 'ProofOfDeliveryDate'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'ROUTE' THEN 'Route'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'VKORG' THEN 'SalesOrganization'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'VOLEH' THEN 'VolumeUnit'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'VOLUM' THEN 'Volume'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'PKSTK' THEN 'PackingStatus'
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'KOSTK' THEN 'IsPicked'            
    END                                                           AS "Attribute",
    CASE
        WHEN "CDPOS"."VALUE_OLD" LIKE '%-' THEN CONCAT('-', REPLACE(LTRIM("CDPOS"."VALUE_OLD"), '-', ''))
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'KOSTK' AND "CDPOS"."VALUE_OLD" != 'C' THEN CAST(FALSE AS VARCHAR(255))
        ELSE "CDPOS"."VALUE_OLD"
    END                                                           AS "OldValue",
    CASE
        WHEN "CDPOS"."VALUE_NEW" LIKE '%-' THEN CONCAT('-', REPLACE(LTRIM("CDPOS"."VALUE_NEW"), '-', ''))
        WHEN "CDPOS"."FNAME" = 'KOSTK' AND "CDPOS"."VALUE_NEW" = 'C' THEN CAST(TRUE AS VARCHAR(255))
        ELSE "CDPOS"."VALUE_NEW"
    END                              AS "NewValue",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "CDHDR"."MANDANT" || '::' || "CDHDR"."USERNAME"  AS "ChangedBy",
    "CDHDR"."TCODE"                                               AS "OperationType",
    "CDHDR"."CHANGENR"                                            AS "OperationID",
    CASE
    WHEN "USR02"."USTYP" IN ('B', 'C') THEN 'Automatic'
    ELSE 'Manual' END                                         AS "ExecutionType"
    FROM "CDPOS" AS "CDPOS"
    LEFT JOIN "CDHDR" AS "CDHDR"
            ON "CDPOS"."MANDANT" = "CDHDR"."MANDANT"
                AND "CDPOS"."OBJECTCLAS" = "CDHDR"."OBJECTCLAS"
                AND "CDPOS"."OBJECTID" = "CDHDR"."OBJECTID"
                AND "CDPOS"."CHANGENR" = "CDHDR"."CHANGENR"
                AND "CDPOS"."OBJECTCLAS" = 'LIEFERUNG'
    LEFT JOIN "LIKP" AS "LIKP"
            ON "CDPOS"."TABKEY" = "LIKP"."MANDT" || "LIKP"."VBELN"
    LEFT JOIN "USR02" AS "USR02"
            ON "CDHDR"."USERNAME" = "USR02"."BNAME"
                AND "CDHDR"."MANDANT" = "USR02"."MANDT"
WHERE (("CDPOS"."TABNAME" = 'LIKP'
    AND "CDPOS"."FNAME" IN ('BTGEW', 'BZIRK', 'GEWEI', 'KODAT', 'LFART', 'LFDAT', 'NTGEW', 'PODAT', 'ROUTE', 'VKORG',
                            'VOLEH', 'VOLUM'))
    OR ("CDPOS"."TABNAME" = 'VBUK'
        AND "CDPOS"."FNAME" IN ('PKSTK', 'KOSTK')))
  AND "CDPOS"."CHNGIND" = 'U'
  AND "LIKP"."VBTYP" = 'J'
  AND "CDPOS"."MANDANT" IS NOT NULL
  AND "CDHDR"."MANDANT" IS NOT NULL
  AND "LIKP"."MANDT" IS NOT NULL

SELECT <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || "LIKP"."MANDT" || '::' || "LIKP"."VBELN"                AS "ID",
    CAST("LIKP"."ERDAT" AS DATE) + CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("LIKP"."ERZET" AS DATE),
                    "LIKP"."ERZET") AS INTERVAL SECOND)                      AS "CreationTime",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || "LIKP"."MANDT" || '::' || "LIKP"."ERNAM"   AS "CreatedBy",
    CASE
        WHEN "USR02"."USTYP" IN ('B', 'C') THEN 'Automatic'
        ELSE 'Manual' END                                                    AS "CreationExecutionType",
    "LIKP"."LFART"                                                           AS "DeliveryType",
    CAST("LIKP"."KODAT" AS DATE) + COALESCE(CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("LIKP"."KOUHR" AS DATE),
        "LIKP"."KOUHR") AS INTERVAL SECOND), INTERVAL '1' SECOND)            AS "PlannedPickingDate",                      
    CAST("LIKP"."PODAT" AS DATE) + COALESCE(CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, CAST("LIKP"."POTIM" AS DATE),
        "LIKP"."POTIM") AS INTERVAL SECOND), INTERVAL '1' SECOND)            AS "ProofOfDeliveryDate",
    CAST("LIKP"."LFDAT" AS TIMESTAMP)                                        AS "DeliveryDate",
    "LIKP"."NTGEW"                                                           AS "NetWeight",
    "LIKP"."BTGEW"                                                           AS "GrossWeight",
    "LIKP"."GEWEI"                                                           AS "WeightUnit",
    "LIKP"."VOLUM"                                                           AS "Volume",
    "LIKP"."VOLEH"                                                           AS "VolumeUnit",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || '::' || "LIKP"."MANDT"                             AS "SourceSystemInstance",
    "LIKP"."VBELN"                                                           AS "DeliveryNumber",
    CAST("LIKP"."WADAT" AS TIMESTAMP)                                        AS "PlannedGoodsIssueDate",
    CASE WHEN "VBUK"."KOSTK" = 'C' THEN TRUE ELSE FALSE END                  AS "IsPicked"
FROM "LIKP" AS "LIKP"
LEFT JOIN "USR02" AS "USR02"
    ON "LIKP"."MANDT" = "USR02"."MANDT"
        AND "LIKP"."ERNAM" = "USR02"."BNAME"
LEFT JOIN "VBUK" AS "VBUK"
    ON "LIKP"."MANDT" = "VBUK"."MANDT"
        AND "LIKP"."VBELN" = "VBUK"."VBELN"
WHERE "LIKP"."MANDT" IS NOT NULL
  AND "LIKP"."VBTYP" = 'J'

WITH "CTE_Delivery" AS (
    SELECT 
        "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DeliveryId"                                                AS "DELIVERY_ID",
        "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DeliveryLinePEODeliveryDetailId"                         AS "DELIVERY_DETAIL_ID",
        "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOTransactionId"               AS "TRANSACTION_ID",
        "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DeliveryLinePEORequestedQuantity"                        AS "REQUESTED_QUANTITY",
        ABS("MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOTransactionQuantity")    AS "TRANSACTION_QUANTITY"
    FROM "FscmTopModelAM_WshDeliveriesAM_DeliveryPVO" AS "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_WshBiccExtractAM_DeliveryLineAssignmentExtractPVO" AS "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"
            ON "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DeliveryId" = "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"."DeliveryLineAssignmentPEODeliveryId"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_WshBiccExtractAM_DeliveryLineExtractPVO" AS "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"
            ON "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"."DeliveryLineAssignmentPEODeliveryDetailId" = "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DeliveryLinePEODeliveryDetailId"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_InvBiccExtractAM_InventoryTransactionDetailExtractPVO" AS "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"
            ON "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DeliveryLinePEOTransactionId" = "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOTransactionId"
    WHERE "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOTransactionId" IS NOT NULL
        AND "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DeliveryLinePEOSourceLineType" = 'SALES_ORDER'
),
"CTE_AGG_Delivery" AS (
    SELECT 
        "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"         AS "DELIVERY_ID",
        MAX("Delivery"."TRANSACTION_ID") AS "TRANSACTION_ID",
        'RELEASED_STATUS'                AS "FNAME",
        'Y'                              AS "RELEASED_STATUS"
    FROM "CTE_Delivery" AS "Delivery"
    GROUP BY "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"
    HAVING SUM("Delivery"."REQUESTED_QUANTITY") = SUM("Delivery"."TRANSACTION_QUANTITY")
),
"CTE_Picked_Confirm" AS (
    SELECT 
        "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID" || "AGG_Delivery"."FNAME"
        || "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOCreationDate"
        || "AGG_Delivery"."RELEASED_STATUS"                                                  AS "ID",
        "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"                                                         AS "ObjectID",
        "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOCreationDate"                    AS "Time",
        CASE
            WHEN "AGG_Delivery"."FNAME" = 'RELEASED_STATUS' 
                THEN 'PickingStatus'
        END                                                                                  AS "Attribute",
        'Unknown'                                                                            AS "OldValue",
        CAST("AGG_Delivery"."RELEASED_STATUS" AS VARCHAR(255))                               AS "NewValue",
        CAST("MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOCreatedBy" AS VARCHAR(255)) AS "ChangedBy",
        NULL                                                                                 AS "OperationType",
        NULL                                                                                 AS "OperationID",
        CASE
            WHEN "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DeliveryPEORequestId" IS NOT NULL THEN 'Automatic'
                ELSE 'Manual'
        END                                                                                  AS "ExecutionType"
    FROM "CTE_AGG_Delivery" AS "AGG_Delivery"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_WshDeliveriesAM_DeliveryPVO" AS "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"
            ON "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID" = "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DeliveryId"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_InvBiccExtractAM_InventoryTransactionDetailExtractPVO" AS "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"
            ON "AGG_Delivery"."TRANSACTION_ID" = "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."InventoryTransactionPEOTransactionId"
    WHERE "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DeliveryId" IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT 
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::'|| "Picked_Confirm"."ObjectID"             AS "ObjectID",
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::'||  "Picked_Confirm"."ID"                  AS "ID",
    "Picked_Confirm"."Time"                                              AS "Time",
    "Picked_Confirm"."Attribute"                                         AS "Attribute",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OldValue"                                          AS "OldValue",
    "Picked_Confirm"."NewValue"                                          AS "NewValue",
    <%=sourceSystem%>  || '::'|| "Picked_Confirm"."ChangedBy"            AS "ChangedBy",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OperationType"                                     AS "OperationType",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OperationID"                                       AS "OperationID",
    "Picked_Confirm"."ExecutionType"                                     AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "CTE_Picked_Confirm" AS "Picked_Confirm"

WITH "CTE_Delivery" AS (

        "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."TRANSACTION_ID"            AS "TRANSACTION_ID",

        ABS("MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."TRANSACTION_QUANTITY") AS "TRANSACTION_QUANTITY"
    FROM "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES" AS "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"
        LEFT JOIN "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS" AS "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"

                    = "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"."DELIVERY_ID"

                ON "WSH_DELIVERY_ASSIGNMENTS"."DELIVERY_DETAIL_ID"
                    = "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."DELIVERY_DETAIL_ID"
        LEFT JOIN "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS" AS "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"
                ON "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."TRANSACTION_ID"
                    = "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."TRANSACTION_ID"
    WHERE "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."TRANSACTION_ID" IS NOT NULL
        AND "WSH_DELIVERY_DETAILS"."SOURCE_CODE" = 'OE'
),

    SELECT
        "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"         AS "DELIVERY_ID",

        'Y'                              AS "RELEASED_STATUS"

    GROUP BY "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"
    HAVING SUM("Delivery"."REQUESTED_QUANTITY") = SUM("Delivery"."TRANSACTION_QUANTITY")
),

        "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"                                   AS "ObjectID",

        CASE
            WHEN "AGG_Delivery"."FNAME" = 'RELEASED_STATUS'
            THEN 'IsPicked'
        END                                                            AS "Attribute",
        CAST(FALSE AS VARCHAR(255))                                    AS "OldValue",
        CAST(TRUE AS VARCHAR(255))                                     AS "NewValue",
        CAST("MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."CREATED_BY" AS VARCHAR(255)) AS "ChangedBy",
        NULL                                                           AS "OperationType",
        NULL                                                           AS "OperationID",
        CASE
            WHEN "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."REQUEST_ID" IS NOT NULL THEN 'Automatic'
            ELSE 'Manual'

    FROM "CTE_AGG_Delivery" AS "AGG_Delivery"
    LEFT JOIN "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES" AS "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"
        ON "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID" = "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_ID"
    LEFT JOIN "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS" AS "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"
        ON "AGG_Delivery"."TRANSACTION_ID" = "MTL_MATERIAL_TRANSACTIONS"."TRANSACTION_ID"
    WHERE "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_ID" IS NOT NULL

    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::'|| "Picked_Confirm"."ObjectID"     AS "ObjectID",
	<%=sourceSystem%> || '::'|| "Picked_Confirm"."ID"           AS "ID",
    "Picked_Confirm"."Time"                                      AS "Time",
    "Picked_Confirm"."Attribute"                                 AS "Attribute",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OldValue"                                  AS "OldValue",
    "Picked_Confirm"."NewValue"                                  AS "NewValue",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::'|| "Picked_Confirm"."ChangedBy"    AS "ChangedBy",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OperationType"                             AS "OperationType",
    "Picked_Confirm"."OperationID"                               AS "OperationID",
    "Picked_Confirm"."ExecutionType"                             AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "CTE_Picked_Confirm" AS "Picked_Confirm"

"CTE_AGG_Delivery" AS (
    SELECT 
        "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID" AS "DELIVERY_ID"
    FROM "CTE_Delivery" AS "Delivery"
    GROUP BY "Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"
    HAVING SUM("Delivery"."REQUESTED_QUANTITY") = SUM("Delivery"."TRANSACTION_QUANTITY")
)
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> 
    || '::' || CAST( "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_ID" AS VARCHAR(255))   AS "ID",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."CREATION_DATE"                                   AS "CreationTime",
    <%=sourceSystem%> 
    || '::' || TRY_CAST("WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."CREATED_BY" AS FLOAT)        AS "CreatedBy",
    CASE
        WHEN "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."BATCH_ID" IS NOT NULL THEN 'Automatic'
        ELSE 'Manual' -- https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E18727_01/doc.121/e13431/T414830T414837.htm#T414957 (autocreated)
    END                                                                    AS "CreationExecutionType",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_TYPE"                                   AS "DeliveryType",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."INITIAL_PICKUP_DATE"                             AS "PlannedPickingDate",
    "WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS"."POD_DATE"                                         AS "ProofOfDeliveryDate",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERED_DATE"                                  AS "DeliveryDate",
    CAST("WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."NET_WEIGHT" AS FLOAT)                       AS "NetWeight",
    CAST("WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."GROSS_WEIGHT" AS FLOAT)                     AS "GrossWeight",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."WEIGHT_UOM_CODE"                                 AS "WeightUnit",
    CAST("WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS"."VOLUME" AS FLOAT)                            AS "Volume",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."VOLUME_UOM_CODE"                                 AS "VolumeUnit",
    CAST("WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."NAME" AS VARCHAR(255))                      AS "DeliveryNumber",
    "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."LATEST_PICKUP_DATE"                              AS "PlannedGoodsIssueDate",
    CASE
        WHEN "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID" IS NOT NULL THEN TRUE
        ELSE FALSE
    END                                                                    AS "IsPicked",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                      AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES" AS "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"
LEFT JOIN "WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS" AS "WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS"
    ON "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_ID" = "WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS"."DELIVERY_ID"
        -- In Oracle there could be a 1:n relationship from delivery to legs.
        -- This means, that one delivery could have many POD
        -- According to etrm received quantity indicates the last leg of a delivery, therefore we take only that POD
        AND "WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS"."RECEIVED_QUANTITY" IS NOT NULL
LEFT JOIN "CTE_AGG_Delivery" AS "AGG_Delivery"
    ON "WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES"."DELIVERY_ID" = "AGG_Delivery"."DELIVERY_ID"
